{
  "chapter": 43,
  "chapter_summary": "第四十三回奇峰迭起：小鱼儿在江岸暗中观察，发现三条黑衣人（海四爹、海红珠及同伴）与双狮镖局李家父子对峙。黑衣人自称仁义三侠，使用梅花钩兵器，揭露赵全海与厉峰中毒后双狮镖局趁机接镖的阴谋。江玉郎突然现身，以高强武功轻松击败三人，揭下海红珠面纱。小鱼儿伪装成鬼魂吓走江玉郎，救下海红珠等人。随后小鱼儿跳江逃生，被段合肥的女儿段三姑娘（女孟尝）的药船救起。小鱼儿凭借对药材的精通获得段三姑娘赏识，被聘到安庆庆余堂药铺工作。段三姑娘告知小鱼儿，双狮镖局所保的段合肥镖银已被劫走，且镖银是半夜神秘失踪的。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_li_di",
      "speaker_name": "金狮李迪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三位可就是自称'仁义三侠'的么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_jin_li_di",
      "text": "不错！",
      "tone": "冷冷",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_li_di",
      "speaker_name": "金狮李迪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "敝镖局的镖车，近年来数次失手，都是三位做的手脚？",
      "tone": "质问",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_jin_li_di",
      "text": "哼",
      "tone": "冷冷",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_li_di",
      "speaker_name": "金狮李迪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三位既然连连得手，我等又查不出三位的来历。三位便该好生躲藏才是，却又为何要下书将我兄弟约来这里？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_jin_li_di",
      "text": "江湖中都已知道，赵全海与厉峰已双双中毒，他们的人虽未死，但两河联镖与三湘镖联的威信却已大伤。",
      "tone": "缓缓",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ting",
      "speaker_name": "紫面狮李挺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这与我等又有何关系？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_li_ting",
      "text": "三湘与两河威信受损，双狮镖局自然可乘机窜起，段合肥那批镖银，自然要着落在你身上了。",
      "tone": "缓缓",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这趟镖关系非浅，双狮镖局想也不敢自力承担，必定请得有旁人从中保证，以我三人之力，只怕也动不了它。",
      "tone": "缓缓",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_mian_shi",
      "speaker_name": "紫面狮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你倒也聪明！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_zi_mian_shi",
      "text": "所以我今日就要叫你们也保不了这趟镖，三湘镖联与两河联镖就算倒了楣，你们也休想占便宜！",
      "tone": "厉喝",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_jin_li_di",
      "text": "你们居然还认得这件兵刃，总算不错！",
      "tone": "道",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ting",
      "speaker_name": "紫面狮李挺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们居然敢将这兵刃亮出来，真可算胆子不小，你们难道就不怕你家仇人不声不响的摘走你们的脑袋？！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_li_ting",
      "text": "没有人会知道梅花钩又已重现江湖的！",
      "tone": "道",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "矮壮黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_li_ming_sheng",
      "text": "这是先还你的！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ming_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "李明生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还我的？",
      "tone": "失声",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位姑娘也用布蒙住脸，是因为生得太丑？还是太美呢？",
      "tone": "笑道",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们既不愿说，在下也只有自己来瞧了。",
      "tone": "笑道",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_hai_hong_zhu",
      "text": "但愿姑娘生得美些，否则在下就失望了。",
      "tone": "笑道",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ming_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "李明生",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "是她！原来是她！",
      "tone": "失声",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_li_ming_sheng",
      "text": "你认得她？",
      "tone": "道",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ming_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "李明生",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "她就是那卖艺的女子，白凌霄大哥就是为她死的那矮子想必就是那天被我掴了一掌的人，难怪他要找我报仇！",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "更妙了，更妙了，梅花门下，居然做了江湖卖艺的，你们为了避仇，居然不惜做如此低贱之事，这点我倒也佩服。",
      "tone": "笑道",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_si_die",
      "speaker_name": "海四爹",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你放开她的手！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_hai_si_die",
      "text": "放开她的手也可以，但我却要先问你，那日一掌就打死白凌霄白公子的人究竟是谁？此刻在哪里？",
      "tone": "道",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_hong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "海红珠",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你想找他，你这是在做梦！",
      "tone": "娇呼",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_hai_hong_zhu",
      "text": "哦，做梦？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_hong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "海红珠",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "像你这样的人和他比起来，连提鞋都不配。",
      "tone": "咬牙",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_si_die",
      "speaker_name": "海四爹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "罢了！",
      "tone": "长叹",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "我的神枢穴疼呀，江玉郎，你还我命来！",
      "tone": "凄声",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "黑心贼，我与你无冤无仇，你却在四海春的厨房里，下毒手害死了我，你赔命来吧。",
      "tone": "咯咯笑",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你想跑？你跑不了的跑不了的，快拿命来吧！",
      "tone": "龇牙笑",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_hong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "海红珠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是你！小呆，是你么？",
      "tone": "脱口大呼",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你还想杀我？你已杀死过我一次，再也杀不死我了！",
      "tone": "阴森笑",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你再也杀不死我了，此刻你难道还不信？",
      "tone": "龇牙笑",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "我不想杀你实在不想杀你！",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_hong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "海红珠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小呆，我知道还能见着你的，我知道",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hai_hong_zhu",
      "text": "谁是小呆我是鬼鬼",
      "tone": "咯咯笑",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_hong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "海红珠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若不想见我，为什么要到这江边来你若想见我，为什么见了我又要走？为什么为什么？",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "船上人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这小子命长，幸好遇见我们，还没淹死。",
      "tone": "笑道",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "大汉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这人是死的？还是活的？",
      "tone": "洪亮",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "活的！",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "大汉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你既是活的。为何要装死？",
      "tone": "大声",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你既是女人，为何又要装成男的？",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_san_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "段三姑娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你知道我是谁？",
      "tone": "怒",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_duan_san_gu_niang",
      "text": "不管你是男的还是女的，你反正是个人，你已经快嫁不出去，再这么凶，还有谁敢娶你！",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_san_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "段三姑娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你敢对我这样说话？",
      "tone": "拍案",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_duan_san_gu_niang",
      "text": "为什么不敢，只要你是人，我就不",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_duan_san_gu_niang",
      "text": "呀，原来你就是段合肥的女儿，你爹爹可是有一批银子要运到关外去？",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_duan_san_gu_niang",
      "text": "这船药材，是你从关外运来的么？",
      "tone": "耸鼻",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_san_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "段三姑娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你怎知道这是船药材？",
      "tone": "瞪眼",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_duan_san_gu_niang",
      "text": "我不但知道这是船药材，还知道这些药材是人参、桂皮、鹿角、五味子",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_san_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "段三姑娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "想不到你这小子对药材还内行得很。",
      "tone": "悠悠",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_duan_san_gu_niang",
      "text": "我对药材非但内行，而且敢说很少有人比我再内行的。你若真的是女孟尝，就该好生将我礼聘到你家的药铺里去。",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_san_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "段三姑娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "替他换件衣服，送他到庆余堂去。",
      "tone": "道",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_san_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "段三姑娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "喂，起来。",
      "tone": "道",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_duan_san_gu_niang",
      "text": "我的名字可不叫喂。",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_san_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "段三姑娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "喂，我问你，上次你说的那批要送到关外的镖银，你怎会知道的？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_duan_san_gu_niang",
      "text": "那批镖银怎样？",
      "tone": "道",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_san_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "段三姑娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "那批银子已被人劫走了。",
      "tone": "冷冷",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "奇怪！既是双狮镖局接的镖，怎么还会被人劫走呢？",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_san_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "段三姑娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "双狮镖局保的镖，怎么就不能被人劫走？哼，我瞧那两个姓李的，根本就是饭桶！",
      "tone": "冷冷",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_duan_san_gu_niang",
      "text": "劫镖的是些什么人，你可知道？",
      "tone": "道",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_san_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "段三姑娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "那批镖银乃是半夜中忽然失踪的，门未开，窗未动，看守镖银的人连屁都未听见，镖银就好像生了翅膀飞了。",
      "tone": "道",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_duan_san_gu_niang",
      "text": "这倒是奇案除非那劫镖银的人会五鬼搬运法，否则就是双狮镖局的人眼睛耳朵有了毛病。",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_san_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "段三姑娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "那他们就活该自己倒楣！",
      "tone": "道",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_duan_san_gu_niang",
      "text": "难道他们要赔？",
      "tone": "道",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_san_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "段三姑娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "当裤子也得赔的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这要怪了我本来还以为这是双狮镖局监守自盗，但他们既然要赔，这又是为了什么呢？",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_san_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "段三姑娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "只因为他们都是饭桶，所以镖银就被人劫走，这道理岂非简单得很。",
      "tone": "道",
      "chapter": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
